text: Laura Lahtinen (born 3 June 2003) is a Finnish swimmer. She competed in the women's 400 metre freestyle and the women's 200 metre butterfly at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Finnish female freestyle swimmers Category:Female butterfly swimmers
